main event: A report from October 25, 1958, in Yucca Valley, California, documented contact with flying discs, including 2 photos.
interesting points: The report includes 2 photographs of the flying discs.
The objects in the photos appear as rectangular shapes with a white appearance against a dark, grainy background.
The lettering 'R.C.M.' and the numbers '1.1.79' are visible on the photographic negatives or slides.
The sighting took place in Yucca Valley, California, an area known for UFO activity.
The report indicates contact with multiple flying discs, suggesting a possible UFO encounter.
